---
title: Mushroom and Leek Linguine with Thyme, Garlic and Parmesan
description: All the elements in this dish are classics that are made for one another. Mushrooms, leeks and thyme have nothing but love for one another and couldn't pair better with a creamy sauce and pasta. Enjoy!
